{"tid":722294,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今屆世界盃小組賽各數據統計  烏龍球、補時致勝球皆創新高","createTime":"2018-06-29T11:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T13:01:47.000Z","uid":110761,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4b249e426528398e3540330f069503aa39d3651b","tid":722294,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"小組賽數據統計<br />\n<br />\n進球最多：比利時（9粒）<br />\n失球最多：巴拿馬（11粒）<br />\n射門最多：德國（72次）<br />\n傳球最多：西班牙（2277次）<br />\n控球時間最多：西班牙（217分鐘）<br />\n犯規最多：韓國（63次）<br />\n被射門次數最多：墨西哥（59次）<br />\n進球最多：哈利簡尼/英格蘭（5粒）<br />\n射門最多：尼馬/巴西（16次）<br />\n撲救最多：奧祖亞/墨西哥（17次）<br />\n犯規最多：馬斯查蘭奴/阿根廷；久巴/俄羅斯（11次）<br />\n被侵犯最多：尼馬/巴西（17次<br />\n<br />\n本屆世界杯烏龍球大行其道，小組賽階段就出現了9次，超越了法國世界杯6次烏龍球的紀錄。目前，烏龍球的進球數量依然高於本屆世界杯射手榜上的所有球員。"},{"pid":"aa9fb14463a33a1f9a2d1ff92ee13709a318379c","tid":722294,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"神射手OG"},{"pid":"7ce7825fa438edc9290c78381818fc94db663e49","tid":722294,"uid":1723,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"黃牌最多呢？"},{"pid":"8e3dcd2165f32f48b09f93d9f0c3372269c2cb31","tid":722294,"uid":11254,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"射門最多：德國（72次）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92dfd562b69efc0682d359087f4c7a5d275af66","tid":722294,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"被侵犯最多：尼馬/巴西（17次）"},{"pid":"b9265e3efa8e6db0f1f951e04ba27a53fe836f8e","tid":722294,"uid":49144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c92dfd562b69efc0682d359087f4c7a5d275af66","tid":722294,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"被侵犯最多：尼馬/巴西（17次）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"屁馬"},{"pid":"ffcb5d84768806f08146